WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.500
This video shows the menu on a tablet or smartphone.

00:03.000 --> 00:06.500
You can easily change the language of the menu.

00:09.000 --> 00:11.500
Learn more about a dish by selecting it.

00:12.000 --> 00:15.000
The European allergen codes or the origin of the ingredients can be seen.

00:16.000 --> 00:21.000
Scroll through the entire menu or navigate through the individual categories.

00:24.000 --> 00:29.000
For example, you can use a filter to highlight dishes that do not contain gluten.

00:30.000 --> 00:34.000
Images can also be displayed in full screen.